False reports like these lead people to miss the real threats of being lured into trafficking. Many people are lured through #socialmedia #peers or #boyfriends  
“Woman could face charges after lying in viral post about attempted luring at Pasco Walmart.”

data.description: According to Pasco Police, a woman’s viral post about her child almost being taken from the Walmart off Road 68 is false. data.title: Woman could face charges after lying in viral post about attempted luring at Pasco Walmart
